sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Admin
    participant TSE as TSE
    participant SM as Security Module
    participant Storage as Storage Medium

    Admin->>TSE: Login as Admin
    TSE-->>Admin: Login successful
    
    Admin->>TSE: setDescription(description)
    activate TSE
    
    Note over TSE: Check: Admin authenticated
    
    TSE->>TSE: Validate description:<br/>- Length <= 64 characters
    
    alt Description too long
        TSE-->>Admin: Exception:<br/>ErrorParameterTooLong
    else Description valid
        TSE->>Storage: Save Description
        activate Storage
        
        alt Saving failed
            Storage-->>TSE: Error
            TSE->>TSE: Reset description<br/>to previous state
            TSE-->>Admin: Exception:<br/>ErrorStoringDataFailed
        else Saving successful
            Storage-->>TSE: OK
            deactivate Storage
            
            TSE->>SM: Create setDescription System Log
            activate SM
            SM->>SM: Log Data:<br/>- description<br/>- eventTriggeredByUser
            SM->>SM: signatureCounter++
            SM->>SM: Create Signature
            SM-->>TSE: Log Message + Signature
            deactivate SM
            
            TSE->>Storage: Save setDescription Log
            activate Storage
            Storage-->>TSE: OK
            deactivate Storage
            
            TSE->>TSE: Update info.csv:<br/>description field
            
            TSE-->>Admin: Description set
        end
    end
    deactivate TSE
    
    Note over Admin,Storage: New description will<br/>be visible in exports
